Hindi pa nga kami kasal...

625
00:44:47,977 --> 00:44:49,729
at ilang beses ka nang inatake.

626
00:44:51,272 --> 00:44:52,815
At nang lumabas ang balita ng paghihiwalay,

627
00:44:54,734 --> 00:44:56,152
Mas lalo lang itong lalala.

628
